# Admin Screens Development Rules

Rules for developing admin pages with Glassmorphism design.

## Admin Routes

```
webui/src/routes/(app)/admin/
├── +layout.svelte         # Admin layout with navigation
├── monitoring/            # LLM monitoring dashboard
├── datacloud/             # Database connector management
├── mcp/                   # MCP server management
├── gateway/               # Kong Gateway overview
├── users/                 # User management
├── settings/              # Settings
└── evaluations/           # Leaderboard
```

