## Color Palette

| Usage | Light | Dark |
|-------|-------|------|
| Primary | `bg-primary text-white` | `bg-primary/90 text-white` |
| Primary subtle | `bg-primary/10 text-primary` | `bg-primary/20 text-primary-light` |
| Success | `bg-green-100 text-green-700` | `bg-green-900/30 text-green-400` |
| Error | `bg-red-100 text-red-700` | `bg-red-900/30 text-red-400` |
| Warning | `bg-amber-100 text-amber-700` | `bg-amber-900/30 text-amber-400` |

## Key Requirements

- Always use Glassmorphism: `backdrop-blur-sm bg-white/60 dark:bg-gray-800/60`
- Support dark mode for all elements
- Use consistent spacing: `p-4`, `p-6`, `gap-4`
- Use rounded corners: `rounded-lg`, `rounded-xl`, `rounded-2xl`
- Add transitions: `transition-all`

